md:
giải nghĩa từ "medical" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

1. Medical (adjective)
	* Meaning: Relating to medicine or the treatment of illnesses.
	* Vietnamese: Y tế
	* Example sentence: The medical team worked tirelessly to save the patient's life.
	* Related words: medicine, doctor, hospital, treatment, health

2. Medical (noun)
	* Meaning: A medical examination or check-up.
	* Vietnamese: Khám bệnh
	* Example sentence: I have a medical tomorrow morning to check my blood pressure.
	* Related words: examination, check-up, doctor, hospital, health

Note: The word "medical" can have different meanings depending on the context in which it is used. The above explanations are two common meanings of the word.
